er"], ["20 June – 10 July", "02 August", "Fall semester"], ["10 October – 10 November", "10 December", "Spring semester"]], "row_count": 3, "column_count": 3, "section_path": ["Guidelines for Student Financial Aid Support Request", "3. Timelines"], "page_number": null, "rag_text": "Table: Guidelines for Student Financial Aid Support Request\nColumns: Column 1 | Column 2 | Column 3\nRow 1: Column 1: Application period | Column 2: Processing deadline | Column 3: Effective semester\nRow 2: Column 1: 20 June – 10 July | Column 2: 02 August | Column 3: Fall semester\nRow 3: Column 1: 10 October – 10 November | Column 2: 10 December | Column 3: Spring semester", "content_hash": "179ee7859e2e07092e857f8886332d897af3d22253ba756da2c46c46cf59090b"}, "metadata": {"source_kind": "financial_policy", "source_id": "ff995913d7d93a383fce19584fb9d044c340666a67bd356761ddd658aa7fe934", "canonical_url": "https://policy.vinuni.edu.vn/all-policies/guidelines-for-student-financial-support-request/", "document_title": "Guidelines for Student Financial Aid Support Request", "domain": "policy.vinuni.edu.vn", "domain_type": "policy", "source_trust": "official_high", "category": "student_affairs", "subcategory": "financial", "parser_name": "crawler", "parser_version": "v3", "source_url": "https://policy.vinuni.edu.vn/all-policies/guidelines-for-student-financial-support-request/", "final_url": "https://policy.vinuni.edu.vn/all-policies/guidelines-for-student-financial-support-request/", "crawl_depth": 0, "discovered_from": "seed", "http_status": 200, "content_type": "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "mime_type": "text/html", "file_size_bytes": 50535, "fetched_at": "2026-06-20T03:07:56.172578+00:00", "robots_allowed": true, "requires_login": false, "noindex": false, "access_level": "public", "crawl_run_id": "2f55a9b8-0bc8-4015-8aac-656a596ffa66", "reference_number": "GDL-FAO-001-V2.0", "document_status": "Guideline", "issuing_unit": "Financial Aid Office", "issued_date": "Apr 22, 2025", "applying_for": "All VinUniversity", "security_classification": "Public", "pdf_url": "https://policy.vinuni.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/GDL-FAO-001-V2.0_Guideline-for-Student-Financial-Support-Request_22.04.2025.pdf", "link_count": 13}}, {"record_id": "1bb0baa22d9090c7a3cea25a09c6f1b07e1d93302fdd2cad513ee760e5416e15", "record_type": "table_record", "parent_doc_id": "ff995913d7d93a383fce19584fb9d044c340666a67bd356761ddd658aa7fe934", "source_url": "https://policy.vinuni.edu.vn/all-policies/guidelines-for-student-financial-support-request/", "title": "Guidelines for Student Financial Aid Support Request", "data": {"table_id": "0165b966b8a801529a2935e0ed75608582e484021bf12d3ea3ad6794f2ff820b", "caption": null, "headers": ["Column 1", "Column 2", "Column 3"], "rows": [["Steps", "Action", "Detailed Explanation"], ["1", "Gather Required Documentation", "Before submitting the request, students should collect all required documents, including: Completed Financial Support Application Form (Link: Home (vinuni.edu.vn) , section Request for FA) Proof of financial need Any additional supporting documents (e.g., letters explaining special circumstances or medical bills)."], ["2", "Submit Financial Support Request", "Submit the request online through the student portal. Ensure all the required documentations are attached. Deadlines : All students: July 10th (for the Fall semester) and November 10th (for the Spring semester) each year. Global Exchange Student Ambassador Grant: Based on the exchange nomination release timelines. Students can apply for the GESA grant after they are nominated for an exchange program by VinUni."], ["3", "Initial Review by Financial Aid Office (FAO)", "FAO will review the application for completeness and eligibility. If their application is incomplete, the student will be notified within 03 working days."], ["4", "Review by Financial Aid Review Committee", "The committee, consisting of university staff and faculty, will evaluate the requests based on: Financial need Academic standing Availability of resources Special circumstances The students meeting the eligibility of each type of grants Review duration : 05 working days after receiving the review request from the Financial Aid Office."], ["5", "Notification of Decision", "Students will be notified via email or the student portal within two working days after the Financial Aid Review Committee makes the final decision. The notification will include: Decision (approved, denied, or request for further documentation) Amount awarded (if applicable) Instructions for next steps"], ["6", "Disbursement of Funds", "Approach for the disbursement of funds as below: For tuition fees : The allocated funds will be directly applied to offset the tuition fees and reflected in the student’s billing statement. For non-tuition fees : Approved funds will be disbursed to the student’s VND bank account for relevant expenses. If the approved funds are to be disbursed to a parent or relative, the student must provide official authorization designating the recipient. The disbursement process and procedures will follow the current university financial and payment regulations. Detailed instructions will be provided to students to ensure clarity and compliance."]], "row_count": 7, "column_count": 3, "section_path": ["Guidelines for Student Financial Aid Support Request", "4. Financial Support Request Procedures"], "page_number": null, "rag_text": "Table: Guidelines for Student Financial Aid Support Request\nColumns: Column 1 | Column 2 | Column 3\nRow 1: Column 1: Steps | Column 2: Action | Column 3: Detailed Explanation\nRow 2: Column 1: 1 | Column 2: Gather Required Documentation | Column 3: Before submitting the request, students should collect all required documents, including: Completed Financial Support Application Form (Link: Home (vinuni.edu.vn) , section Request for FA) Proof of financial need Any additional supporting documents (e.g., letters explaining special circumstances or medical bills).\nRow 3: Column 1: 2 | Column 2: Submit Financial Support Request | Column 3: Submit the request online through the student portal. Ensure all the required documentations are attached. Deadlines : All students: July 10th (for the Fall semester) and November 10th (for the Spring semester) each year. Global Exchange Student Ambassador Grant: Based on the exchange nomination release timelines. Students can apply for the GESA grant after they are nominated for an exchange program by VinUni.\nRow 4: Column 1: 3 | Column 2: Initial Review by Financial Aid Office (FAO) | Column 3: FAO will review the application for completeness and eligibility. If their application is incomplete, the student will be notified within 03 working days.\nRow 5: Column 1: 4 | Column 2: Review by Financial Aid Review Committee | Column 3: The committee, consisting of university staff and faculty, will evaluate the requests based on: Financial need Academic standing Availability of resources Special circumstances The students meeting the eligibility of each type of grants Review duration : 05 working days after receiving the review request from the Financial Aid Office.\nRow 6: Column 1: 5 | Column 2: Notification of Decision | Column 3: Students will be notified via email or the student portal within two working days after the Financial Aid Review Committee makes the final decision. The notification will include: Decision (approved, denied, or request for further documentation) Amount awarded (if applicable) Instructions for next steps\nRow 7: Column 1: 6 | Column 2: Disbursement of Funds | Column 3: Approach for the disbursement of funds as below: For tuition fees : The allocated funds will be directly applied to offset the tuition fees and reflected in the student’s billing statement. For non-tuition fees : Approved funds will be disbursed to the student’s VND bank account for relevant expenses. If the approved funds are to be disbursed to a parent or relative, the student must provide official authorization designating the recipient. The disbursement process and procedures will follow the current university financial and payment regulations. Detailed instructions will be provided to students to ensure clarity and compliance.", "content_hash": "dde2b5007fe1e4b75b1d7a5bd36c579d0e347cc93065cd297045e1fa0ab4676c"}, "metadata": {"source_kind": "financial_policy", "source_id": "ff995913d7d93a383fce19584fb9d044c340666a67bd356761ddd658aa7fe934", "canonical_url": "https://policy.vinuni.edu.vn/all-policies/guidelines-for-student-financial-support-request/", "document_title": "Guidelines for Student Financial Aid Support Request", "domain": "policy.vinuni.edu.vn", "domain_type": "policy", "source_trust": "official_high", "category": "student_affairs", "subcategory": "financial", "parser_name": "crawler", "parser_version": "v3", "source_url": "https://policy.vinuni.edu.vn/all-policies/guidelines-for-student-financial-support-request/", "final_url": "https://policy.vinuni.edu.vn/all-policies/guidelines-for-student-financial-support-request/", "crawl_depth": 0, "discovered_from": "seed", "http_status": 200, "content_type": "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "mime_type": "text/html", "file_size_bytes": 50535, "fetched_at": "2026-06-20T03:07:56.172578+00:00", "robots_allowed": true, "requires_login": false, "noindex": false, "access_level": "public", "crawl_run_id": "2f55a9b8-0bc8-4015-8aac-656a596ffa66", "reference_number": "GDL-FAO-001-V2.0", "document_status": "Guideline", "issuing_unit": "Financial Aid Office", "issued_date": "Apr 22, 2025", "applying_for": "All VinUniversity", "security_classification": "Public", "pdf_url": "https://policy.vinuni.edu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/GDL-FAO-001-V2.0_Guideline-for-Student-Financial-Support-Request_22.04.2025.pdf", "link_count": 13}}, {"record_id": "4fd27356a9c8fa19bf6a0b0847f6bbc43bb1d366c943425a1ffd747b46269447", "record_type": "table_record", "parent_doc_id": "ff995913d7d93a383fce19584fb9d044c340666a67bd356761ddd658aa7